{"title":"麦","date":"2022-02-27T13:26:17.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Feb 27, 2022","L":"02/27/2022","MM-DD":"02-27"},"thumbnail":"https://cdn.wardzhou.art/img/wheat-g7653d74e0_1280.webp","link":"2022/02/27/Wheat","comments":true,"tags":["诗"],"categories":["诗"],"updated":"2022-02-27T14:16:00.918Z","content":"<p>麦芒一簇簇地<br>\n在雨后的灿阳下<br>\n攒动</p>\n<p>还在远处<br>\n突然被这风<br>\n送来的热浪<br>\n偷袭</p>\n<p>带着分明的<br>\n沉重，清爽<br>\n不顾一切</p>\n<p>不觉间<br>\n顽皮的孩子<br>\n已唱着歌<br>\n自顾自儿地<br>\n跑进麦田</p>\n<p>歌声渐远，<br>\n孩子也消失在<br>\n涌动的麦浪</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Y.L.</p>\n</blockquote>\n","prev":{"title":"Hue","link":"2022/08/07/Hue"},"next":{"title":"2021年，我镜头下的人","link":"2022/02/03/2021Photograph"},"plink":"http://wardzhou.art/2022/02/27/Wheat/","reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"Birch","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International(<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0/\" rel=\\\"external nofollow\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)","updated":"February 27, 2022"},"reading_time":"82 words in 1 min"}